\h GODS \d

For your reference, the following is a list of the gods worshiped by the inhabitants of Rumia. More information can be found about these gods in-game.

Name      | God of              | Personification
----------+---------------------+----------------
Aule      | wealth              | male dwarf
Caila     | the harvest         | female human
Celoriel  | psionics            | female lagomorph
Dellio    | debauchery          | female felinoid
Drogo     | the moon and magic  | male hobbit
Iminye    | art and engineering | female elf
Itulvatar | light               | none
Murgorhd  | darkness            | none
Rhayk     | war                 | male vulpenoid
Rumialys  | nature              | male nymph

\uSEE ALSO\n
calendar, sacrifice
